package model
  • Class
    Description
    AdminRole
    AdminRole class contains the methods to handle admin responsibility like performing administrative tasks and access sensitive system functionalities.
    Branch
    The Branch class is a class in the Model layer that represents a branch of the restaurant.
    BranchDataManager
    The BranchDataManager handles the interaction between the application and the database.
    EmployeeDataManager
    The EmployeeDataManager handles the interaction between the application and the employee database.
    EmployeeFilter
    The EmployeeFilter class handles the filtering of employees by various criteria.
    EmployeeHandler
    The EmployeeHandler class responsible for managing employees and providing access to employee data.
    FilterOrder
    FilterOrder class contains the methods of handling different filter types for filtering Orders
    ManagerRole
    The ManagerRole contains the methods to handle the responsibilities of the manager in the ordering system.
    MenuDataManager
    The MenuDataManager handles the interaction between the application and the database.
    Order
    The Order class is a class in the Model layer that represents an Order instance.
    Order.OrderStatus
    The OrderStatus enumeration represents the states of an Order.
    ResetPassword
    The ResetPassword handles the interaction between the application and the database.
    StaffRole
    StaffRole class contains the methods to handle staff responsibility in the ordering system.
